    'name' => 'marine_weather',
    'description' => 'Fetch marine weather data from the free Open-Meteo Marine API (no API key required). Returns wave height, wave direction, wave period, swell height/direction/period, ocean current velocity/direction, and sea surface temperature. Provides current conditions with human-readable wave/swell descriptions and daily summaries. First ocean/marine data capability in the ecosystem. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
    'parameters' => 
    array (
      'type' => 'object',
      'properties' => 
      array (
